 highly recommended to try some of their best dishes. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--visa \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--visa\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/get-visa-myanmar\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Order your Visa for Myanmar here<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155739\/Things-to-do-Mandalay-Myanmar-Mingalarbar-dinner.jpg\" alt=\"Things to do Mandalay Myanmar Mingalarbar dinner\"><\/noscript><img width=\"441\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Things to do Mandalay Myanmar Mingalarbar dinner\" class=\"wp-image-6482 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155739\/Things-to-do-Mandalay-Myanmar-Mingalarbar-dinner.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155739\/Things-to-do-Mandalay-Myanmar-Mingalarbar-dinner-300x230.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155739\/Things-to-do-Mandalay-Myanmar-Mingalarbar-dinner-600x460.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155739\/Things-to-do-Mandalay-Myanmar-Mingalarbar-dinner-441x338.jpg 441w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/23155739\/Things-to-do-Mandalay-Myanmar-Mingalarbar-dinner-783x600.jpg 783w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\